title: 3 Story Chic **Townhome**!  2 Car Garage!
posting_body: ['Reside on the edge of uptown Dallas and in the middle of all the culture, fashion and business you can take in.', 'Tap into an authentic big-city lifestyle complete with sparkling skyline views and plenty of well-designed apartment and townhome floorplans.', 'Your urban adventure awaits.', ' 1 & 2 bedroom apartments and townhomes today!', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES...', 'Resort-Inspired Pool', 'Controlled Access Community', 'Covered and Garage Parking Available', 'Night Patrol', 'Free Weights', 'Coffee Bar Lounge with Complementary Wifi', 'Fitness Center with State-of-the-Art Equipment', 'Executive Business Center & Conference Room', 'Direct Elevator Access', 'Spectacular Skyline Views', 'APARTMENT AMENTIES...', 'Expansive 10 to 18-Foot Ceilings', 'Ceiling Fans with Energy-Efficient Lighting', 'Oversized Walk-In Closets', 'Full Sized Washers and Dryers', 'Wood-Style Flooring', 'Energy Star Appliance Package', 'Open-Concept Living Areas', 'Fully-Equipped Gourmet Kitchens with Prep Islands', 'Contemporary Track Lighting in Kitchen and Dining Spaces', 'Energy-Efficient, Dual Pan Windows', 'Private Patio or Balcony', 'Custom Wood Cabinetry', 'Select Three-Story Townhomes with Attached Two-Car Garages', 'Additional Exterior Storage Available', 'Please Call Desiree with DASH Realty', 'show contact info', '**Mention AD 150']
